Name: Professor Hewel
Text: Advisor, please welcome William to the team. Our objective is the Parking Lot

Name: William
Text: Thank-you Professor! I'm happy to help the COSC department once more.

Name: William
Text: I guess getting to Finance won't be easy.

Name: Professor Hewel
Text: Nothing has been the same since Banktania attacked.

Name: Professor Hewel
Text: William we need you and the Academic Advisor to get to the parking office

Name: Professor Hewel
Text: Without access to the parking lot, we'll have to rely on our students to go in on foot.

Name: William
Text: If they only just took over the parking lot, the forces there must be small.

Name: William
Text: And with my advisor, I know that we'll win! Let's go!
